\s NDAGUSABA MANA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ndagusaba Mana\bd*\bd  yanjye uri mw’Ijuru kujya uduhora iruhande buri munsi kubera yuko Satani yatwibasiye ashaka ukuntu yadusubiza inyuma. \bd*
\pc \bdit Dufate ukuboko Mwami utoyobore inzira tuyobore inzira nziza igana mw’Ijuru.\bdit*\bdit x2\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Aha mw’isi duhorana amagorwa menshi kubera kwirengagiza Ijambo ryawe ni yo mpamvu Mana yacu tugusaba y’uko waduha amatwi yo kumva ibibwirizwa. \bd*
\pc \bdit Dufate ukuboko Mwami utoyobore inzira tuyobore inzira nziza igana mw’Ijuru.\bdit*\bdit x2\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ibigusha byinjiye mw’Itorero ryawe isi yacu igenda isaza buri munsi ni yo mpamvu dusaba Yesu kutuba iruhande kuko igihe cy’imperuka kiri hafi.\bd*\bd x2\bd*\bd  \bd*
